The rune dart tip is a dart tip made with the Smithing skill. Players can craft this item by using a rune bar on an anvil with a hammer in the inventory and a Smithing level of 89. Each bar creates 10 dart tips, yielding 75 experience. They can be fletched into rune darts at level 81 Fletching when used with feathers, granting 188 Fletching experience per 10 darts made.

To smith darts, one must have completed the Tourist Trap quest.

They can be fletched into [[rune dart]]s at level 81 Fletching when used with [[feather]]s, granting 188 Fletching experience per 10 darts made.

To smith darts, one must have completed the [[Tourist Trap]] quest.
